'''''Yoga for You''''' is a television series produced by Urban Brew Studios and broadcast from [[India]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/ancient-healing-dr-pankaj-naram-and-secrets-for_us_59b4152ae4b0bef3378ce09a|title=Ancient Healing, Dr. Pankaj Naram, and Secrets for Helping in Natural Disasters|last=Pucchi|first=Rani St|date=2017-09-09|website=Huffington Post|language=en-US|access-date=2017-09-10}}</ref> The television station [[Zee TV network]] was fined 25,000 pounds due to the claims made by [[Pankaj Naram]] on the show and the station subsequently stopped showing it.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Jackson|first1=Jasper|title=Hindi TV channel fined £25,000 over cancer cure claims on yoga show|url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2015/jul/29/hindi-tv-channel-fined-cancer-cure-claims-yoga-show-ofcom|accessdate=12 September 2017|work=The Guardian|date=29 July 2015}}</ref>

